"9 781591 418849 9 0 0 0 0 ISBN 1-5914-1884-4 Structured for Results. Like an elegant tapestry, a complicated, structured beauty exists inside mathematics. To fully grasp its beauty, you must peel back its layers to reveal its essence—its core. Saxon Math Course 3 contains a distinct look and approach that reveal and develop the core of mathematics. More importantly, our core positions students for success."
